cff-version: 1.2.0
message: >-
  If you use phase_mnv_rs, please cite this software and explicitly cite the
  variant-normalization paper whose left-aligned + parsimonious representation
  is implemented here: Tan, Abecasis, and Kang (2015), DOI
  10.1093/bioinformatics/btv112.
title: phase_mnv_rs
type: software
